1
00:00:05,805 --> 00:00:09,074
His agency probably
gathered all that info for him.

2
00:00:09,075 --> 00:00:10,977
You could learn a thing
or two from him, Cousin.

3
00:00:12,278 --> 00:00:13,846
Let me see...

4
00:00:13,847 --> 00:00:17,851
Why doesn't Hei Yan drive?

5
00:00:19,119 --> 00:00:20,387
A car accident?

6
00:00:21,054 --> 00:00:23,089
It was that serious?

7
00:00:23,390 --> 00:00:24,991
Where did the object pierce?

8
00:00:26,459 --> 00:00:27,619
Just thinking about it hurts.

9
00:00:57,357 --> 00:00:58,491
What are you doing?

10
00:00:59,325 --> 00:01:00,460
What am I doing?

11
00:01:00,860 --> 00:01:01,895
I...

12
00:01:02,095 --> 00:01:03,430
I...

13
00:01:11,371 --> 00:01:12,705
You have a fever!

14
00:01:12,972 --> 00:01:14,307
I have a fever?

15
00:01:16,342 --> 00:01:17,243
You're burning up.

16
00:01:17,244 --> 00:01:18,278
We should head back.

17
00:01:18,511 --> 00:01:19,412
No, it's fine.

18
00:01:19,413 --> 00:01:20,693
I'll be okay after a quick rest.

19
00:01:21,181 --> 00:01:22,881
Didn't you just nap?

20
00:01:22,882 --> 00:01:23,983
Why aren't you better?

21
00:01:24,684 --> 00:01:26,885
It was hard to schedule. Don't change it.

22
00:01:26,886 --> 00:01:27,886
Let's go.
